abstract: >-
  us-fashion-persona is a local-first tool for pre-screening US fashion
  product concepts with synthetic personas, structured product cards, official
  U.S. aggregate-statistics context, LLM evaluation, validation, aggregation,
  and Markdown/CSV reports.
